<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Six_Degrees_of_Kevin_Bacon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.gladwell.com/1999/1999_01_11_a_weisberg.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.gladwell.com/1999/1999_01_11_a_weisberg.htm" rel="nofollow">Six Degrees of Lois Weisberg</a> - Suggests that Bacon connects to many actors because he acts in many different kinds of roles and films.</li>
<li>A nice looking implementation of <a href="http://www.thekevinbacongame.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.thekevinbacongame.com/" rel="nofollow">The Kevin Bacon Game Online</a></li>
<li>The <a href="http://oracleofbacon.org/" class="external text" title="http://oracleofbacon.org/" rel="nofollow">Oracle of Bacon at the University of Virginia</a> computes the Bacon number of any actor or actress from IMDb data</li>
<li><a href="http://www.cinfn.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.cinfn.com/" rel="nofollow">Cinema FreeNet Movie Connector</a> finds links between stars, but can also use directors and producers.</li>
<li><a href="http://cse.unl.edu/~jtooker/projects/cse156/hw5.php" class="external text" title="http://cse.unl.edu/~jtooker/projects/cse156/hw5.php" rel="nofollow">Another oracle of Bacon type game by a computer science student</a></li>
</ul>


